1
00:00:00,600 --> 00:00:01,600
<i> Mom, it's Jade.</i>

2
00:00:01,600 --> 00:00:03,167
<i> Roi kidnapped her.</i>

3
00:00:03,167 --> 00:00:04,267
<i>- Aah!
- Ah!</i>

4
00:00:04,267 --> 00:00:05,633
<i> Help!</i>

5
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:08,267
[JADE YELPS]

6
00:00:08,267 --> 00:00:10,300
<i> Stop being stubborn, Jade.</i>

7
00:00:10,300 --> 00:00:12,300
<i> We trusted him!</i>

8
00:00:12,300 --> 00:00:13,767
<i> He's a monster!</i>

9
00:00:13,767 --> 00:00:16,033
<i> If Roi is the murderer,</i>

10
00:00:16,033 --> 00:00:19,233
<i> it means Papa and Uncle
Fred's friendship was real.</i>

11
00:00:19,233 --> 00:00:20,767
<i> It's payback time.</i>

12
00:00:20,767 --> 00:00:23,700
<i> I can't lose another member
of our family again.</i>

13
00:00:23,700 --> 00:00:27,433
<i>That's why I'll do everything
to get your sister back home.</i>

14
00:00:27,433 --> 00:00:29,233
<i> I'll send you the location.</i>

15
00:00:29,233 --> 00:00:31,333
<i>But Frida, don't pull
a fast one on me,</i>

16
00:00:31,333 --> 00:00:33,033
<i> or I'll kill your daughter.</i>

17
00:00:33,033 --> 00:00:34,033
<i>Aren't we going
to do something?</i>

18
00:00:34,067 --> 00:00:36,367
<i> We can't just sit here
and do nothing.</i>

19
00:00:38,033 --> 00:00:39,267
<i> Leon, listen to me.</i>

20
00:00:39,267 --> 00:00:41,667
<i>No matter what happens,
Jade should be the priority.</i>

21
00:00:41,667 --> 00:00:43,467
<i> I love you all so much.</i>

22
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:52,000
[BROODING MUSIC PLAYING]

23
00:00:54,667 --> 00:00:57,233
I can't just wait here.
I'll go follow them.

24
00:00:57,233 --> 00:00:58,533
Psst. Hey.

25
00:00:58,533 --> 00:01:01,733
Look. We can't just
go there.

26
00:01:01,733 --> 00:01:03,533
The police have a plan.

27
00:01:05,367 --> 00:01:07,600
Earlier, you said
it was dangerous,

28
00:01:07,633 --> 00:01:09,167
and now you want
to go there?

29
00:01:10,667 --> 00:01:12,133
Yes.

30
00:01:12,133 --> 00:01:14,800
But like I said,
you can't stop me.

31
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:16,433
I have to save Jade.

32
00:01:17,267 --> 00:01:18,767
Hey.

33
00:01:18,767 --> 00:01:23,067
If you'll only cause my mother
and sister to get hurt,

34
00:01:23,067 --> 00:01:24,833
then don't help, Edward.

35
00:01:24,833 --> 00:01:26,167
Just go home.

36
00:01:30,467 --> 00:01:31,700
Follow me.

37
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:43,800
[FOREBODING MUSIC PLAYING]

38
00:01:57,133 --> 00:02:04,067
[FOREBODING MUSIC CONTINUES]

39
00:02:06,233 --> 00:02:13,233
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]

40
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:13,767
[BROODING MUSIC PLAYING]

41
00:03:15,700 --> 00:03:18,600
[PHONE RINGING]

42
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:20,567
Hello? Hello, Roi?

43
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:21,567
Where are you?

44
00:03:21,567 --> 00:03:24,233
I'm here at our meeting place.

45
00:03:25,500 --> 00:03:26,900
Are you alone?

46
00:03:26,900 --> 00:03:30,500
Yes. That was our
agreement, right?

47
00:03:30,500 --> 00:03:31,967
I brought my stuff
with me

48
00:03:31,967 --> 00:03:36,867
so I can go with you
wherever you want to take me.

49
00:03:39,967 --> 00:03:41,533
There's a path
on your right.

50
00:03:43,967 --> 00:03:45,233
Go there.

51
00:03:46,433 --> 00:03:48,433
Okay. Jade is with you,
right?

52
00:03:48,433 --> 00:03:50,600
<i> Just do as I say.</i>

53
00:03:51,367 --> 00:03:55,833
[BROODING MUSIC CONTINUES]

54
00:03:55,867 --> 00:03:57,000
[CALL DROPS]

55
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,200
Roi!

56
00:04:03,900 --> 00:04:10,833
[BROODING MUSIC CONTINUES]

57
00:04:19,700 --> 00:04:21,667
Go, hurry. Follow her.

58
00:04:22,633 --> 00:04:23,667
Copy, sir.

59
00:04:29,467 --> 00:04:36,433
[BROODING MUSIC CONTINUES]

60
00:04:47,467 --> 00:04:54,467
[BROODING MUSIC CONTINUES]

61
00:04:56,033 --> 00:04:57,767
Leon should've taken me
with him.

62
00:04:59,033 --> 00:05:00,867
I want to hurt Roi myself!

63
00:05:02,700 --> 00:05:03,967
If there are many
of us there,

64
00:05:03,967 --> 00:05:06,700
Roi might not believe Mom.

65
00:05:06,700 --> 00:05:09,000
This isn't just about
Jade's safety, Justin,

66
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,567
but also Mom's safety.

67
00:05:12,067 --> 00:05:13,900
All we can do
for now

68
00:05:13,900 --> 00:05:16,667
is pray that nothing bad
happens to them.

69
00:05:18,900 --> 00:05:20,633
I hope they call.

70
00:05:20,633 --> 00:05:26,533
[MOROSE MUSIC PLAYING]

71
00:05:26,533 --> 00:05:28,400
I hope Jade and Mom
are okay.

72
00:05:34,567 --> 00:05:35,767
[FRIDA] Roi?

73
00:05:37,733 --> 00:05:39,000
Jade?

74
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:45,500
[UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]

75
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:46,567
[FRIDA GASPS]

76
00:05:51,933 --> 00:05:54,533
- Wait. Where's Jade?
- Shh! Shh!

77
00:05:55,533 --> 00:05:58,833
[UNSETTLING MUSIC CONTINUES]

78
00:05:58,833 --> 00:06:01,800
[ROI BREATHING SHAKILY]

79
00:06:06,767 --> 00:06:13,767
[UNSETTLING MUSIC CONTINUES]

80
00:06:16,867 --> 00:06:19,633
Wait. Roi, wait.

81
00:06:19,633 --> 00:06:22,033
I'm going with you, right?

82
00:06:22,033 --> 00:06:24,533
But first, tell me where
Jade is.

83
00:06:24,533 --> 00:06:25,867
Where's my daughter?

84
00:06:28,867 --> 00:06:30,833
- Would you like to see her?
- Yes, yes.

85
00:06:30,833 --> 00:06:32,367
- Love?
- Yes.

86
00:06:33,667 --> 00:06:34,767
Jade!

87
00:06:34,767 --> 00:06:37,000
Jade, Mommy is here!
Where are you?

88
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:39,033
- Jade!
- Shh! Shh! Shh!

89
00:06:39,033 --> 00:06:41,000
- Jade!
- Shh!

90
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:43,400
Roi, Jade isn't here.

91
00:06:46,533 --> 00:06:48,900
[BREATHES SHARPLY]

92
00:06:50,500 --> 00:06:57,500
[UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]

93
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:05,567
- Is the service boat ready?
- Yes.

94
00:07:05,567 --> 00:07:06,667
You're leaving?

95
00:07:09,767 --> 00:07:11,133
I knew it. You're leaving.

96
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:15,467
I was thinking,
if Leon went with Aunt Frida,

97
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:17,600
who was left
at their house?

98
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:20,733
Probably Luna.
Or maybe Justin.

99
00:07:20,733 --> 00:07:22,467
We all know Justin.

100
00:07:22,467 --> 00:07:23,767
He can be feisty.

101
00:07:23,767 --> 00:07:26,100
I won't be surprised if
he went with Leon.

102
00:07:26,100 --> 00:07:27,433
What's your point?

103
00:07:32,167 --> 00:07:33,967
Luna might be alone.

104
00:07:35,567 --> 00:07:38,600
But they have bodyguards,
remember?

105
00:07:39,767 --> 00:07:43,800
It's still better if there are
other people aside from them.

106
00:07:45,567 --> 00:07:46,900
You're worried about her?

107
00:07:48,500 --> 00:07:51,500
You said it yourself we can't
just sit and do nothing.

108
00:07:51,500 --> 00:07:54,767
I have to do something
and check on them.

109
00:07:54,767 --> 00:07:58,567
Now you understand me when I
want to do something for Jade.

110
00:07:59,833 --> 00:08:01,767
If you're going there,
I'm going too.

111
00:08:01,767 --> 00:08:03,900
- Let's go.
- Me too.

112
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:05,200
I thought you just
wanted to wait.

113
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:07,867
[SCOFFS]
I won't be left alone here.

114
00:08:07,867 --> 00:08:09,500
Come on, we're running
out of time.

115
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:18,967
[STIRRING MUSIC PLAYING]

116
00:08:23,233 --> 00:08:30,233
[DARK MUSIC PLAYING]

117
00:08:39,733 --> 00:08:43,100
You said you'd take me
to Jade, but she's not here.

118
00:08:43,100 --> 00:08:44,900
- Where is my daughter?!
- Love.

119
00:08:44,900 --> 00:08:47,467
Love. Love, listen to me.

120
00:08:48,167 --> 00:08:50,000
We don't need her anymore.

121
00:08:51,767 --> 00:08:54,100
Once we get out
of here,

122
00:08:54,100 --> 00:08:56,167
we'll have her siblings
pick her up.

123
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:59,300
No! That wasn't our agreement.

124
00:08:59,300 --> 00:09:02,267
I want to see my daughter!
Where is Jade?!

125
00:09:02,267 --> 00:09:04,533
- Love. Love.
- Where's Jade?

126
00:09:04,533 --> 00:09:05,700
She's safe.

127
00:09:06,900 --> 00:09:08,733
But you can't see her
anymore.

128
00:09:08,733 --> 00:09:11,900
No! You didn't keep your word!

129
00:09:12,967 --> 00:09:15,067
Where is Jade?!

130
00:09:15,067 --> 00:09:16,600
Where is my daughter?!

131
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:18,733
Jade! Jade!

132
00:09:18,733 --> 00:09:20,033
You're so stubborn!

133
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:25,767
Shh.

134
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:28,200
Love, shh.

135
00:09:28,233 --> 00:09:30,167
Don't be stubborn, okay?

136
00:09:30,967 --> 00:09:32,533
- Roi.
- Don't be stubborn.

137
00:09:34,733 --> 00:09:40,567
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

138
00:09:40,567 --> 00:09:42,733
- Mom!
- Leon!

139
00:09:42,733 --> 00:09:44,067
[ROI] I knew it!

140
00:09:45,567 --> 00:09:48,100
- No.
- Love, you tricked me?

141
00:09:48,100 --> 00:09:50,567
- No.
- You said you'd come with me.

142
00:09:50,567 --> 00:09:52,033
Leon, just go.

143
00:09:52,033 --> 00:09:53,867
Leave now, please.

144
00:09:53,867 --> 00:09:55,267
I'll go with you.

145
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:57,733
Leon, please go.

146
00:09:57,733 --> 00:10:00,333
Suit yourselves if you want
to delay things.

147
00:10:00,333 --> 00:10:02,733
If you'll let Frida and I leave,

148
00:10:02,767 --> 00:10:05,000
you might still find
Jade alive.

149
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,833
Roi, what did you do
to Jade?

150
00:10:07,833 --> 00:10:09,567
What did you do
to my daughter?

151
00:10:10,367 --> 00:10:17,567
[DARK MUSIC PLAYING]

152
00:10:38,167 --> 00:10:45,100
[MUFFLED GRUNTING]

153
00:10:48,800 --> 00:10:50,400
[WHIMPERS]

154
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:51,767
[MUFFLED] Help!

155
00:10:53,633 --> 00:10:54,967
[MUFFLED] Help!

156
00:10:54,967 --> 00:10:57,733
- [MUFFLED SCREAMING]
- [THWACKING]

157
00:10:57,733 --> 00:10:59,633
[MUFFLED] Help!

158
00:11:00,300 --> 00:11:03,233
[MUFFLED] Help!

159
00:11:03,233 --> 00:11:06,300
[MUFFLED SCREAMING]

160
00:11:07,667 --> 00:11:14,400
[MUFFLED SCREAMING]

161
00:11:15,733 --> 00:11:18,300
[MUFFLED SOBBING]

162
00:11:20,467 --> 00:11:25,433
[MUFFLED SCREAMING]

163
00:11:25,433 --> 00:11:26,633
[JADE] Help!

164
00:11:26,633 --> 00:11:29,367
[MUFFLED GASPING]

165
00:11:29,367 --> 00:11:31,133
Help!

166
00:11:32,133 --> 00:11:33,267
Help!

167
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:36,100
[FRIDA] What did you do
to my daughter?

168
00:11:36,100 --> 00:11:37,233
[ROI] My love...

169
00:11:38,067 --> 00:11:39,367
Explain it to them.

170
00:11:39,367 --> 00:11:42,267
Tell them I'm innocent.

171
00:11:43,967 --> 00:11:45,500
- Mom, no.
- Tell them.

172
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:47,433
- Please!
- [FRIDA] No.

173
00:11:47,433 --> 00:11:49,433
- Don't do this, Mom.
- [FRIDA] No.

174
00:11:49,433 --> 00:11:50,433
Leon.

175
00:11:51,300 --> 00:11:53,467
Our priority, remember?

176
00:11:53,467 --> 00:11:57,067
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

177
00:11:57,067 --> 00:11:58,400
My love.

178
00:11:59,667 --> 00:12:02,167
- What are you talking about?
- I'm coming with you.

179
00:12:02,167 --> 00:12:03,400
- No--
- Huh?

180
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:05,067
They won't follow us.

181
00:12:05,067 --> 00:12:06,567
I'm coming with you. Let's go.

182
00:12:06,567 --> 00:12:08,100
Stay right there.

183
00:12:08,100 --> 00:12:09,300
Please!

184
00:12:09,300 --> 00:12:11,100
Don't you dare follow us!

185
00:12:12,533 --> 00:12:13,600
Go!

186
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:16,567
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

187
00:12:17,500 --> 00:12:19,133
- [GRUNTS]
- [BLOW LANDS]

188
00:12:19,133 --> 00:12:20,233
[LEON] Let her go!

189
00:12:20,233 --> 00:12:22,433
[BOTH GROANING]

190
00:12:22,433 --> 00:12:23,767
- Frida!
- Roi!

191
00:12:23,767 --> 00:12:25,733
[GRUNTING]

192
00:12:25,733 --> 00:12:27,567
[BOTH GROANING]

193
00:12:27,567 --> 00:12:29,233
[BLOWS LAND]

194
00:12:30,433 --> 00:12:31,567
[BLOW LANDS]

195
00:12:34,667 --> 00:12:36,467
[BLOWS LAND]

196
00:12:36,467 --> 00:12:37,533
Roi!

197
00:12:37,533 --> 00:12:39,267
Don't hurt my son!

198
00:12:39,633 --> 00:12:40,733
Police!

199
00:12:40,733 --> 00:12:43,633
[TENSE MUSIC SWELLS]

200
00:12:43,633 --> 00:12:45,433
- Get up!
- [FRIDA] Leon!

201
00:12:45,433 --> 00:12:46,667
Don't move!

202
00:12:46,667 --> 00:12:48,267
Don't come any closer!

203
00:12:48,300 --> 00:12:50,033
[LEON CHOKING]

204
00:12:50,033 --> 00:12:51,133
Stay back.

205
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:52,633
[FRIDA] Roi!

206
00:12:53,433 --> 00:12:55,067
Put your guns down

207
00:12:55,067 --> 00:12:56,700
if you want to see Jade alive!

208
00:12:58,067 --> 00:12:59,433
- Leon.
- Put them down!

209
00:12:59,433 --> 00:13:04,700
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

210
00:13:05,533 --> 00:13:07,433
So? Has Leon replied?

211
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:09,233
Not yet.

212
00:13:09,567 --> 00:13:11,167
Maybe we should stop
bothering him.

213
00:13:11,167 --> 00:13:12,667
He'll update us
when something happens.

214
00:13:12,667 --> 00:13:13,533
Oh God.

215
00:13:13,533 --> 00:13:15,700
I hope nothing bad
happened to them.

216
00:13:15,700 --> 00:13:17,300
Nothing's going to happen.

217
00:13:17,300 --> 00:13:18,367
Okay?

218
00:13:18,367 --> 00:13:20,367
Panicking won't help, Kiko.

219
00:13:20,367 --> 00:13:23,033
Sorry, I'm just worried
about Jade.

220
00:13:23,067 --> 00:13:24,500
We're all worried.

221
00:13:26,467 --> 00:13:28,133
Maybe call Luna too?

222
00:13:28,133 --> 00:13:29,600
So she knows we're
on the way.

223
00:13:32,700 --> 00:13:35,833
[LINE BEEPING]

224
00:13:35,833 --> 00:13:37,233
She's not answering.

225
00:13:40,100 --> 00:13:42,200
[LINE BEEPING]

226
00:13:44,800 --> 00:13:46,133
[TIRES SCREECHING]

227
00:13:46,767 --> 00:13:48,167
What the hell?!

228
00:13:48,567 --> 00:13:49,700
[GUN COCKS]

229
00:13:49,700 --> 00:13:52,267
[OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING]

230
00:13:52,267 --> 00:13:53,533
[KIKO] What's his problem?

231
00:13:53,533 --> 00:13:54,633
Is that Bok?

232
00:13:56,467 --> 00:13:58,133
That bastard!
It's Bok!

233
00:13:58,467 --> 00:13:59,533
Gio!

234
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,200
Gio!

235
00:14:03,333 --> 00:14:05,100
If you want to see Jade alive,

236
00:14:05,767 --> 00:14:07,133
let me go!

237
00:14:07,133 --> 00:14:10,300
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

238
00:14:10,300 --> 00:14:11,400
Fine!

239
00:14:13,733 --> 00:14:16,700
[PANTING]

240
00:14:16,700 --> 00:14:17,833
Put them down!

241
00:14:17,833 --> 00:14:24,400
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

242
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:27,600
[LEON GRUNTS]

243
00:14:28,433 --> 00:14:29,567
Secure the area.

244
00:14:32,667 --> 00:14:33,867
Come. Come...

245
00:14:33,867 --> 00:14:35,267
Come on, Leon.

246
00:14:40,767 --> 00:14:42,233
[KIKO BREATHING HEAVILY]

247
00:14:42,233 --> 00:14:44,800
[BOK] Gio, get down here.
Let's settle this!

248
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:48,267
[KIKO BREATHING HEAVILY]

249
00:14:48,733 --> 00:14:49,767
Get down.

250
00:14:51,400 --> 00:14:52,767
Get down here, Gio!

251
00:14:53,633 --> 00:14:55,533
Gio. Gio...

252
00:14:55,533 --> 00:14:57,500
- Gio. Gio. Gio. Gio.
- [KIKO] Gio.

253
00:14:57,500 --> 00:14:58,833
[MARTIN] Gio.

254
00:14:58,833 --> 00:15:00,300
Gio!

255
00:15:00,300 --> 00:15:03,200
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

256
00:15:03,233 --> 00:15:04,367
Get down!

257
00:15:07,833 --> 00:15:09,133
Gio.

258
00:15:11,533 --> 00:15:13,233
[KIKO BREATHING HEAVILY]

259
00:15:13,233 --> 00:15:14,367
[BOK] Get down!

260
00:15:14,367 --> 00:15:21,267
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

261
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,200
Son, are you okay?

262
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:25,400
- The ambulance is on the way.
- Thank you.

263
00:15:25,400 --> 00:15:26,467
Mom.

264
00:15:30,367 --> 00:15:31,600
The ambulance is coming, okay?

265
00:15:32,800 --> 00:15:39,833
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

266
00:15:39,867 --> 00:15:42,833
[PANTING]

267
00:15:43,733 --> 00:15:44,800
[BOK] Get down!

268
00:15:44,800 --> 00:15:45,967
- Gio.
- You should run.

269
00:15:45,967 --> 00:15:48,700
- I'm the only one he's after.
- We're not leaving you!

270
00:15:48,700 --> 00:15:49,900
We're sticking together.

271
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:55,367
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

272
00:15:56,400 --> 00:15:57,533
Stop being stubborn.

273
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:02,667
One, two...

274
00:16:03,300 --> 00:16:04,867
...three, run!

275
00:16:04,867 --> 00:16:06,567
- [GUNSHOT]
- Go after them!

276
00:16:06,567 --> 00:16:07,833
[GUNSHOTS]

277
00:16:08,533 --> 00:16:10,467
You two take those two!
I'll go after Gio!

278
00:16:10,467 --> 00:16:13,300
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

279
00:16:21,567 --> 00:16:22,633
Come here!

280
00:16:22,633 --> 00:16:29,567
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

281
00:16:29,800 --> 00:16:30,900
Hey!

282
00:16:31,533 --> 00:16:34,767
[MAN GRUNTING]

283
00:16:38,267 --> 00:16:39,367
Hey!

284
00:16:42,433 --> 00:16:44,333
- Gio!
- [GUNSHOTS]

285
00:16:45,733 --> 00:16:52,933
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

286
00:16:56,033 --> 00:16:57,867
I'm not after your money
anymore, Gio.

287
00:16:58,867 --> 00:17:00,267
Just do it, Bok.

288
00:17:00,967 --> 00:17:02,900
But don't drag my brothers
into this.

289
00:17:03,533 --> 00:17:05,500
Bogs and the others
will take care of them.

290
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:09,533
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

291
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:12,467
[THUDS]

292
00:17:12,467 --> 00:17:16,267
[GROANING]

293
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:21,267
I'll kill you if anything
happens to them.

294
00:17:21,867 --> 00:17:23,300
You're funny.

295
00:17:23,300 --> 00:17:24,467
You think you can kill me?

296
00:17:24,467 --> 00:17:25,800
Who's holding the gun here?

297
00:17:28,500 --> 00:17:29,500
[GUNSHOT]

298
00:17:30,500 --> 00:17:31,600
[GUNSHOT]

299
00:17:34,700 --> 00:17:35,967
[BLOWS LAND]

300
00:17:35,967 --> 00:17:39,767
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

301
00:17:39,767 --> 00:17:40,833
[BOTH GRUNTING]

302
00:17:42,500 --> 00:17:46,200
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

303
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,267
[GRUNTS]

304
00:17:47,267 --> 00:17:49,267
[BLOWS LAND]

305
00:17:50,633 --> 00:17:52,333
[BOTH GRUNTING]

306
00:17:52,333 --> 00:17:53,533
[THUDS]

307
00:17:53,533 --> 00:17:55,367
[BLOWS LAND]

308
00:17:55,367 --> 00:17:58,400
[GRUNTS]

309
00:17:58,400 --> 00:18:02,867
[BLOWS LAND]

310
00:18:06,500 --> 00:18:07,900
[HEAVY THUD]

311
00:18:07,900 --> 00:18:09,533
[GROANING]

312
00:18:09,533 --> 00:18:11,167
[COUGHS]

313
00:18:11,167 --> 00:18:13,000
[ROI GROANING]

314
00:18:14,567 --> 00:18:17,433
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

315
00:18:18,500 --> 00:18:19,600
[GROANING]

316
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:21,100
Frida!

317
00:18:21,100 --> 00:18:22,900
Frida, help me!

318
00:18:22,933 --> 00:18:24,000
Frida.

319
00:18:24,533 --> 00:18:26,900
- [ROI PANTING]
- Cuff him.

320
00:18:28,067 --> 00:18:29,633
Frida, help me!

321
00:18:29,633 --> 00:18:31,267
- Frida!
- You're under arrest.

322
00:18:31,267 --> 00:18:32,667
You have the right
to remain silent.

323
00:18:32,667 --> 00:18:34,933
Anything you say can
and will be used

324
00:18:34,933 --> 00:18:36,633
against you in court.
Do you understand?

325
00:18:37,400 --> 00:18:39,233
You don't understand me.

326
00:18:39,233 --> 00:18:42,000
Frida... Frida's the only one
who understands me!

327
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:43,067
Frida!

328
00:18:43,067 --> 00:18:44,233
[ROI PANTING]

329
00:18:44,233 --> 00:18:45,933
Where did you take Jade Almazan?

330
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:48,167
Answer me!

331
00:18:48,633 --> 00:18:52,267
Let me talk to Frida alone
before I tell you anything!

332
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:55,000
Go. Take him.

333
00:18:56,233 --> 00:18:57,333
[ROI] Frida!

334
00:18:58,667 --> 00:19:00,567
So what, we're not calling them?

335
00:19:02,267 --> 00:19:03,467
Why is it taking so long?

336
00:19:04,167 --> 00:19:06,233
This is so hard, not knowing
what's happening.

337
00:19:07,933 --> 00:19:09,167
Did they find Roi?

338
00:19:10,267 --> 00:19:11,533
Did they find Jade?

339
00:19:11,533 --> 00:19:14,100
If we call, Justin,
we might ruin their plan.

340
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:15,967
- But what if...
- [SIGHS]

341
00:19:17,233 --> 00:19:19,400
- ...something happened to Jade?
- Shh! No!

342
00:19:20,067 --> 00:19:21,533
Don't even say that.

343
00:19:24,333 --> 00:19:26,233
As long as they haven't said
anything,

344
00:19:26,233 --> 00:19:28,500
nothing bad has happened
to our sister.

345
00:19:29,367 --> 00:19:35,533
[UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]

346
00:19:36,700 --> 00:19:38,133
- Help!
- [THUDS]

347
00:19:38,700 --> 00:19:40,600
[MUFFLED GASPING]

348
00:19:40,600 --> 00:19:42,133
Help!

349
00:19:42,667 --> 00:19:47,467
[MUFFLED SCREAMING]

350
00:19:47,467 --> 00:19:48,600
Help!

351
00:19:51,100 --> 00:19:52,300
[JADE] Help!

352
00:19:53,500 --> 00:19:58,500
[MUFFLED GASPING]

353
00:19:59,167 --> 00:20:06,133
[DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYING]

354
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:20,600
[BLOWS LAND]

355
00:20:20,600 --> 00:20:22,400
[BOTH GRUNTING]

356
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:23,533
[BLOW LANDS]

357
00:20:25,533 --> 00:20:26,967
[BLOWS LAND]

358
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:30,433
[BLOW LANDS]

359
00:20:34,067 --> 00:20:36,733
[GRUNTING]

360
00:20:36,767 --> 00:20:38,267
You're still trying to run?

361
00:20:38,733 --> 00:20:40,400
[BOTH GROANING]

362
00:20:40,400 --> 00:20:41,467
[BLOW LANDS]

363
00:20:42,200 --> 00:20:46,167
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

364
00:20:46,167 --> 00:20:49,100
[BOTH GRUNTING]

365
00:20:50,267 --> 00:20:53,133
[BLOWS LAND]

366
00:20:54,533 --> 00:20:55,700
[BOTH GRUNTING]

367
00:20:55,700 --> 00:21:01,633
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

368
00:21:02,567 --> 00:21:05,267
[GROANING IN PAIN]

369
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:10,300
[GASPING]

370
00:21:14,433 --> 00:21:19,300
[BLOWS LAND]

371
00:21:21,200 --> 00:21:22,800
What? Let's take him
to the boss!

372
00:21:22,800 --> 00:21:24,567
Wait! I'm not done yet!

373
00:21:24,567 --> 00:21:28,133
[BLOWS LAND]

374
00:21:30,700 --> 00:21:34,367
- [BLOWS LAND]
- [YELLING]

375
00:21:34,700 --> 00:21:38,433
- [BLOWS LAND]
- [YELLING]

376
00:21:39,333 --> 00:21:40,633
Kiko! Kiko, stand up!

377
00:21:40,633 --> 00:21:42,200
Kiko! Kiko!

378
00:21:42,233 --> 00:21:44,100
Can you still move?
Let's go!

379
00:21:44,700 --> 00:21:47,600
- [BLOWS LAND]
- [MAN GRUNTS]

380
00:21:47,600 --> 00:21:48,833
That's enough, Kiko!

381
00:21:48,833 --> 00:21:50,700
We have to go back for Gio!

382
00:21:50,700 --> 00:21:52,500
Kiko, come on!

383
00:21:52,500 --> 00:21:53,567
Gio!

384
00:21:53,567 --> 00:21:55,500
We have to find Gio!

385
00:21:56,767 --> 00:22:03,700
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

386
00:22:06,767 --> 00:22:08,067
[BOK GRUNTS]

387
00:22:10,300 --> 00:22:13,500
[GASPING]

388
00:22:13,800 --> 00:22:20,767
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

389
00:22:32,600 --> 00:22:33,767
[GRUNTS]

390
00:22:33,767 --> 00:22:37,300
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

391
00:22:38,867 --> 00:22:43,533
[GLUM MUSIC PLAYING]

392
00:22:43,533 --> 00:22:44,700
[GRUNTS] Argh!

393
00:22:50,767 --> 00:22:52,833
How does it feel
to be unlucky, Gio?

394
00:22:52,833 --> 00:22:54,600
- [BOTH GRUNTING]
- [FLESH SQUELCHES]

395
00:22:54,600 --> 00:22:56,367
[GIO GRUNTS IN PAIN] Agh!

396
00:23:00,067 --> 00:23:03,000
[GRUNTING CONTINUES] Agh!

397
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:09,967
[GLUM MUSIC CONTINUES]

398
00:23:17,567 --> 00:23:19,600
They were dead when I saw them!

399
00:23:19,600 --> 00:23:21,533
<i> Rot in jail, murderer!</i>

400
00:23:21,533 --> 00:23:23,567
<i> I can tell you the truth</i>

401
00:23:23,600 --> 00:23:26,767
<i> with my conscience clear!</i>

402
00:23:26,767 --> 00:23:28,433
[LEAVES RUSLTING]

403
00:23:28,433 --> 00:23:30,100
<i> Don't let go! Hold on tight!</i>

404
00:23:31,033 --> 00:23:32,667
<i> Jade!</i>

405
00:23:32,667 --> 00:23:33,900
[MUFFLED WAIL]

406
00:23:33,900 --> 00:23:35,600
<i> Mom, we need to find Jade.</i>

407
00:23:35,600 --> 00:23:37,767
<i> Did Roi tell you where she is?</i>

408
00:23:37,767 --> 00:23:39,600
<i>Our entire team
is still searching for her.</i>

